extendedInfo.description: EasyPrint is an ad supported print application that allows users to print their documents with their Android devices over the Google cloud. Some features are not yet implemented and will be added to EasyPrint shortly.EasyPrint works over Google Cloud Print.  Google Cloud Print can connect to to any existing printer on Windows or Mac with Internet access that uses the Google Cloud Print connector within the Google Chrome browser. Features:* Works with more than one Google account simultaneously* Print documents from different Android devices* Get list of available printers of account: status, name, properties of printer* Stores list of printers in local storage of device* Remove printers from list* Manage print jobs in queue* Filter and remove print jobs* Print from Google Docs* Share printerkw:google cloud print, cloud print, printing, print, maildroid, printer, HP, laserjet

reviews.title: It worked flawlessly
reviews.comment: Samsung Galaxy Note 10.1. It was very easy to setup. It connects through the Google Cloud Print Service. You will need to set that up first. (Very easy) Once that is done, it found all my printers in my house. I have a wired networked Dell laser printer on a gigabit network and a wireless Brother printer on a wireless \'N\' network. The printing is clear, dark and legible, no driver conflicts. Works seamlessly with Google Cloud Print. It can also send to my Google docs account. It found my 2 phones (HTC One S & LG G2X) I can send anything to my phones though this app. It will also send to Adobe PDF print. It was easy to setup, it did not ask any confusing questions. This is a great app. I would pay for this app. It has small ads that are not intrusive on a tablet screen. Since this is a free app, I click on the ads and have bought something to support the developer.

reviews.title: Used to work before update
reviews.comment: This app worked flawlessly before update.  Now it will not work and says my printer has an error.  I went to Google Cloud and uninstalled my printer and reinstalled.  I did the same thing with this app as well.  Printed test page from Cloud and no issues.  Tried to print from this app, it errors out.  Tried to print from storage section and app crashes.  Sent in crash data.  I can print from my computer if I send it to my email first.  My printer prints flawlessly.  Still cannot print from this app!!!
